***the GET request for the questions list will require the following paramerters***

1. product_id type=integer Specifies the product for which to retrieve questions.

2. page type=integer	Selects the page of results to return. Default 1.

3. count	type=integer Specifies how many results per page to return. Default 5.

***the GET request for the list of answers (does not include reported answers) reqiures the paramerter***

question_id	type=integer Required ID of the question for wich answers are needed

and the following query paramerters

1. page	type=integer Selects the page of results to return. Default 1.

2. count type=integer Specifies how many results per page to return. Default 5.

***the POST request for adding a new question requires the following body paramerters***

1. body type=text	Text of question being asked

2. name type=text	Username for question asker

3. email	type=text	Email address for question asker

4. product_id type=integer Required ID of the Product for which the question is posted

*** the POST request for adding a new answer requires the following paramerters***

1. question_id type=integer required ID of the question to post the answer to.

as well as the following body parameters


